#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn17.37"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.37:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.37:0.2"
msgid "4. Catutthavagga "
msgstr "4. The Fourth Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 37. Mātusutta → mātari (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.37:0.3"
msgid "37. Mātusutta "
msgstr "37. Mother "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.243, sc1
msgctxt "sn17.37:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.37:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko kaṭuko pharuso antarāyiko anuttarassa yogakkhemassa adhigamāya. "
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal, bitter, and harsh. They’re an obstacle to reaching the supreme sanctuary. "

msgctxt "sn17.37:1.3"
msgid "Idhāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi: "
msgstr "When I’ve comprehended the mind of a certain person, I understand: "

msgctxt "sn17.37:1.4"
msgid "‘na cāyamāyasmā mātupi hetu sampajānamusā bhāseyyā’ti. "
msgstr "‘This venerable would not tell a deliberate lie even for the sake of their mother.’ "

msgctxt "sn17.37:1.5"
msgid "Tamenaṃ passāmi aparena samayena lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūtaṃ pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ sampajānamusā bhāsantaṃ. "
msgstr "But some time later I see them tell a deliberate lie because their mind is overcome and overwhelmed by possessions, honor, and popularity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.37:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko kaṭuko pharuso antarāyiko anuttarassa yogakkhemassa adhigamāya. "
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity—bitter and harsh, an obstacle to reaching the supreme sanctuary. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.37:1.7"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "sn17.37:1.8"
msgid "‘uppannaṃ lābhasakkārasilokaṃ pajahissāma. "
msgstr "‘We will give up arisen possessions, honor, and popularity, and we won’t let them occupy our minds.’ "

msgctxt "sn17.37:1.9"
msgid "Na ca no uppanno lābhasakkārasiloko cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassatī’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn17.37:1.10"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.37:1.11"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
